The '''Rozenburg [[Oil refinery|refinery]]''' is an oil refinery owned by Kuwait Petroleum Europort BV which is a subsidiary of [[Kuwait Petroleum International]], KPI. It is sometimes referred to as the Europort refinery. The refinery capacity is 4 mtpa (80 kbpd) of crude oil. And has a [[Nelson complexity index]] of approximately 6.
